那一樣都係死"},{"pid":"b323a33888b2856583faf79096d5f315925e762b","tid":2432003,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019a86ed6a26c173f11cbac9153dc224333ca9eb","tid":2432003,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"出面啲連登仔仲打飛機話支那加速<br />\n事實今次係贏到開巷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"其實有無疫苗外交，呢啲窮撚國家一向都見錢眼開奶支<br />\n睇下舊年邊啲國家支持國安法就知"},{"pid":"06b71428bb115111466a62f36b0401beee97d793","tid":2432003,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:21:58.000Z","msg":"佢話好好好然後唔知點算好"},{"pid":"4a0f5fde3c57be59120f38e10352c68e9d8f3866","tid":2432003,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"208617cbe0637a96a9c8ebcad36f6362f4d26912","tid":2432003,"uid":25468,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:37:56.000Z","msg":"支那疫苗先係最昂貴喎，鱔稿黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"支那堆殺人疫苗全部免費主動送入人地國家門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}